Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.26,0:02:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.26,0:02:52.73,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:57.67,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...head for the New World,\Nthe second half of the Grand Line.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:03.33,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, no one has ever fully explored it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.33,0:03:06.43,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nexcept for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.55,0:03:12.57,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The New World has ruined\Nmany pirates' dreams and ambitions.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.59,0:03:17.49,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.49,0:03:20.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,turned to rubber after \Nhe ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.71,0:03:22.38,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and his friends venture into that sea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.11,0:03:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To take down one of the Four Emperors -\Nthe rulers of the New World,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.54,0:03:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others formed a \Npirate alliance with Trafalgar Law
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.55,0:03:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and have come to Dressrosa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.62,0:03:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They freed the toys who had \Nbeen forced to labor as slaves{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.17,0:03:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but Doflamingo trapped everybody \Nin the country in the Birdcage{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.27,0:03:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and put prices on the heads \Nof Luffy and 11 others.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.38,0:03:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You have no time to wonder what to do.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.26,0:03:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}People are falling and\Ntowns are burning moment by moment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.07,0:04:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Either you kill me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.00,0:04:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...or kill the 12 criminals.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.11,0:04:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now the game is on!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.44,0:04:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our plan was to destroy the SMILE factory
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.45,0:04:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and provoke a conflict between\NDoflamingo and Kaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.85,0:04:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if we kill Doflamingo now,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.05,0:04:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NKaido will direct all his anger over losing SMILEs,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.55,0:04:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.79,0:04:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll have to fight face-to-face\Nwith the angry Emperor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.48,0:04:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not an issue now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.41,0:04:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a good look at this country!\NIf I stop now, what's gonna happen to it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.97,0:04:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Issho-{\i1}san{\i0}, don't we need \Nto capture Doflamingo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.74,0:04:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Restrain as many out-of-control people\Nas possible
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and focus on Straw Hat and \NLaw's pirate alliance!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.65,0:04:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:04:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Send that message to all units!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.00,0:05:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.60,0:05:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He who shoots oft at last \Nshall {\i1}not{\i0} hit the mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy admiral!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.29,0:05:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The gambling old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.39,0:05:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"With a Rumbling of the Ground!\NThe God of Destruction - Giant Pica Descends!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.62,0:06:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go kick Doflamingo's ass!\NGet out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.32,0:06:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are quite brash. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.07,0:06:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm not going to step aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.61,0:06:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an unpleasant chore this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:52.05,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,THE ROYAL PALACE
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.07,0:06:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doflamingo-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.94,0:06:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat Luffy and the \Nothers are clashing with
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.70,0:06:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NFujitora and Navy soldiers at this very moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.25,0:07:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? Let them fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.99,0:07:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy and the pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.42,0:07:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you allow me to create havoc...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.83,0:07:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}--The voice!\N--His voice is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.73,0:07:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can take care all of them by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.74,0:07:24.71,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,PICA - A TOP EXECUTIVE \NOF THE DON QUIXOTE FAMILY
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.81,0:07:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His voice is so high!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.43,0:07:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How could a giant man like that\Nhave such voice!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.39,0:07:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh no... I still can't get used to it
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.63,0:07:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Neven though I've heard it so many times!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.98,0:07:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But if I burst out laughing, he'll kill me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.22,0:07:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in no hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.80,0:07:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, this game is like an \Nelection to select the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.63,0:07:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked the nation of Dressrosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.67,0:07:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is more fit to be their king?\NIs it the Riku Family or the Don Quixote Family?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.47,0:08:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People choose their king.\NIt's their legitimate right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.44,0:08:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's bothersome!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.45,0:08:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You idiot!\NDo you want him to kill you?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.11,0:08:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should just get rid of all the pests!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.19,0:08:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hold it! You have to hold it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.92,0:08:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All we have to do is\Nrepel the ones who are coming
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.76,0:08:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and sit back and watch the \Nothers kill each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.53,0:08:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doffy! I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.58,0:08:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! I-I'm sorry, Pica-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.12,0:08:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive him!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.95,0:08:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's new and he was sort \Nof taken by surprise...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.37,0:08:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.34,0:08:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna bury you alive!\NYou'll be stuck in stones...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.48,0:08:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Pica-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.65,0:08:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Armsmorphosis!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.69,0:08:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gatling Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.47,0:08:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you handle it,\Nyou'll destroy his body completely!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.97,0:09:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then his family can't bury him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.74,0:09:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Baby 5!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.73,0:09:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.03,0:09:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a family?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.67,0:09:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.07,0:09:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.04,0:09:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes, me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.57,0:09:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost my mother when I was eight\Nand killed my father when I was ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.95,0:09:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The members who are ranked
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.17,0:09:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as executives and above are\Nmy family who I've been
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.04,0:09:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,through thick and thin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.40,0:10:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are all I've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.03,0:10:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive anyone who laughs at my family!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.25,0:10:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.67,0:10:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.81,0:10:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Five-star - Usopp is in the Colosseum!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.11,0:10:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That way! Go after him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.71,0:10:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.59,0:10:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.92,0:10:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usoland is a man of 500 million!\NEverybody wants him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.55,0:10:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our legendary hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.25,0:10:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not something to be proud of!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.10,0:10:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have to accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.15,0:10:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody can help chasing after a star...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.30,0:10:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nlike me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.47,0:10:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.99,0:10:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A round of applause!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.64,0:10:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You guys...\N--Stop fooling around and hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.45,0:10:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-{\i1}san{\i0}, how can we get \Nto the King's Plateau?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of the geographical \Nshift, the outer wall of
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.95,0:11:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Colosseum is connected to the plateau!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.36,0:11:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we climb from there,\Nwe can meet up with the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.86,0:11:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Found them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're increasing in number!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.76,0:11:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna take care of them all at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.34,0:11:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hack-{\i1}san{\i0}?!\N--Leave them up to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.57,0:11:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.61,0:11:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You money-blinded idiots!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.53,0:11:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you people \Nknuckle under to Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.61,0:11:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Four Thousand Brick Fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.59,0:11:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.56,0:11:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Rebecca, you go ahead!\N--Robin-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.13,0:11:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.90,0:11:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bartolomeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.57,0:11:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thrilled to hear \NRobin-{\i1}senpai{\i0} call my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.71,0:11:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm gonna hold the enemies back here
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:11:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so please go ahead with Sniper King-{\i1}senpai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.97,0:12:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.45,0:12:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-{\i1}senpai{\i0} thanked me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.22,0:12:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all fired up now!\NI'm not gonna let anyone go after them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.02,0:12:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stand in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.24,0:12:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You used the strange technique again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.80,0:13:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no... We have no role to play here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.68,0:13:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back to\Nthe Young Master-{\i1}sama{\i0} for now-{\i1}in{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.12,0:13:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.\NOh? Where did Se√±or go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.15,0:13:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know how he is-{\i1}in{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.12,0:13:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must be looking for that pervert
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.71,0:13:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nto have some kind of a hard-boiled face-off-{\i1}in{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.93,0:13:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hard-boiled face-off?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.66,0:13:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me, Little People!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.77,0:13:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna {\i1}super{\i0} destroy the SMILE factory
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.61,0:13:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nand save you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.94,0:13:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we're here but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.68,0:13:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do we climb up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.42,0:13:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Count on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.91,0:13:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cien Fleurs!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.02,0:13:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spider Net!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.24,0:14:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.71,0:14:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A round of applause!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.34,0:14:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You guys did it again...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.68,0:14:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Leo, you guys go first!\N--Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.85,0:14:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bartolomeo-{\i1}san{\i0}! Hack-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.47,0:14:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can climb up from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.95,0:14:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.49,0:14:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I climb up there,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.17,0:14:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0} and \NZoro-{\i1}senpai{\i0}, can't I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.76,0:14:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.30,0:14:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The key to Law's handcuffs \Nshould be somewhere...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.38,0:14:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.99,0:14:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father-{\i1}sama{\i0}, Rebecca and \Nthe others are down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.94,0:14:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.89,0:14:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is the criminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.18,0:14:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.26,0:15:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.87,0:15:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.51,0:15:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tank!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.17,0:15:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.76,0:15:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Tank, will guard you with my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.05,0:15:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! That's Captain Tank!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.72,0:15:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King Riku-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.72,0:15:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that he's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.59,0:15:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandfather-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.99,0:15:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.69,0:15:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait for me, everybody!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will take back the real Dressrosa!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.88,0:16:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.90,0:16:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.48,0:16:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Is this the junkyard?\N--Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.93,0:16:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As its name suggests,\Nthere's trash everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.31,0:16:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's going on out there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.54,0:16:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.41,0:16:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, do you people know\Na samurai warrior named Kanjuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.19,0:16:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanjuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.66,0:16:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.37,0:16:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.64,0:16:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.07,0:16:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they up to this time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's happening again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.76,0:17:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.13,0:18:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Is that...\N--Finally, he shows up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.37,0:19:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When that guy emerges, it's all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.41,0:19:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can fight back anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.30,0:19:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.84,0:19:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A giant man?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.44,0:19:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gigantic!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.91,0:19:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pica!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.45,0:19:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pica-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.81,0:19:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.66,0:20:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, those of you who rebel \Nagainst our family...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.51,0:20:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.93,0:20:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna fight you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.77,0:20:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His voice! It's so high!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.22,0:20:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it totally doesn't fit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.05,0:20:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a funny voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.47,0:20:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-P-P-Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.75,0:20:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, stop laughing, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.70,0:20:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pica-{\i1}sama{\i0} is sensitive about \Nhis high-pitched voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.36,0:20:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he runs wild with that massive body...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.41,0:21:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! You made Pica-{\i1}sama{\i0} mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.05,0:21:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you guys not laugh at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.77,0:21:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't!\NBecause we don't wanna die yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.92,0:21:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.06,0:21:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just a punch!\NIt's like a part of the town falling onto us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.90,0:21:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Pica is pissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.94,0:21:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's head for the Palace as we run-{\i1}in{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.39,0:21:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so thrilling!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.98,0:21:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel something terrible is happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.75,0:22:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Issho-{\i1}san{\i0}, please run!\NA giant stone man is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.20,0:22:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! You have to stop messing\Nwith your enemies...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.35,0:22:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.06,0:22:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See! You can't help laughing either!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.67,0:22:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.70,0:22:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.49,0:22:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run! It's gonna crush you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.35,0:22:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}am{\i0} running!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.28,0:22:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.22,0:23:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.89,0:23:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The super-giant Pica smashes up\NLuffy and the others!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.84,0:23:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Facing this worst-ever enemy,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.97,0:23:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the warriors who once \Nfought against each other
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.11,0:23:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to the death in the Colosseum \Ncome together and join Luffy,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.16,0:23:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and the group of unique \Ncharacters who are looking to
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.66,0:23:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,take down Doflamingo, start \Nmaking a significant advance!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.86,0:23:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.42,0:23:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Gathering into a Powerful Front!\NLuffy and a Group of Brutal Warriors!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.53,0:23:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.79,0:23:48.79,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,
